ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "This is a really yummy dip for gingersnap or molasses cookies! It goes on like frosting and smells like the holidays! Refrigerate until serving. Enjoy!"
ins: Combine cream cheese, powdered sugar, and pumpkin pie spice in bowl; add whipped topping and beat until blended.
